extendedInfo.description: JQ99 (99.3 FM) is West Michigan's hit Christian music station playing songs from artists like Chris Tomlin and Casting Crowns to Francesca Battistelli and Jeremy Camp. Download the JQ99 App for your Android device. Listen on the go as you interact with JQ99 through their Music, Events, and much more! Play the radio in the background while you enjoy other Apps or surf the web. The JQ99 App was created exclusively for listeners like YOU who want to take YOUR radio station with you wherever you are. Be sure to tell your friends that you've got the new JQ99 Android App!
